Description: Proxmox VE storage plugin for NetApp ONTAP NVMe/TCP
 Exposes NetApp ONTAP NVMe namespaces as direct block devices for
 Proxmox VE virtual machines over NVMe/TCP.
 .
 Architecture: 1 VM disk = 1 NVMe namespace = 1 FlexVol volume.
 Multi-disk VMs use ONTAP consistency groups for atomic snapshots.
 .
 Requires ONTAP 9.10.1+ and PVE 8.x/9.x (APIVER >= 11).
